Edit: I am... Floored. Flabbergasted. Overwhelmed by how much love y'all have poured out for me. I feel like I've been brought into the biggest and most loving family and have gained all the wonderful parents, brothers and sisters I never thought I'd have. I'm truly, honestly just completely and utterly overwhelmed.

I hope, I really and genuinely hope that if one thing comes from what I thought would just be me yelling into the void to a luke-warm nonresponse, it's that someone - maybe you reading this - feels like you can accept yourself for who you are. You don't have to scream it out loud like I did, you don't even have to tell anyone if you don't want to or you can't for whatever reason, but I hope you accept yourself and know that there are many, many people out there who wish you nothing but the absolute best, who love you for who you are, who you want to be the you you really are. Whatever that means, be it gay, bi, pan, ace, trans, enby, genderfluid... Love yourself, and embrace who you are.

You are absolutely not alone. Take it from this overwhelmed, crying trans girlie - you are absolutely not alone, and we love you.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6pG20Pg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MythIncarnate]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I have several questions</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HdQh76t</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0lE42UA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HdQh76t</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hugs***</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9UbYoNx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cLZNHVc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you’re going through a hard time and need someone to talk to, feel free to dm anytime</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9UbYoNx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[nt99gma3zp365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Accounts for everything under the Sun.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jlEDj7V</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JTCPmzg.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jlEDj7V</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ProfessorGigglesworth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How many glasses do you need??</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CCtovWt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zRkiSRx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CCtovWt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[willpostanything]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>But Google is never wrong</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AGXpOqJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kkX4YED.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; heig